       pb-aggiungi-LinkTo.
      * <TOTEM:PARA. pb-aggiungi-LinkTo>
           perform TOTALE-RIGHE. 
           add 1 to tot-righe giving riga.
              
           modify  form1-gd-1, insert-rows = 1.                

           initialize bat-rec replacing numeric data by zeroes
                                   alphanumeric data by spaces.
                                          
           add 1        to LastPrg.
           move LastPrg to bat-prg col-prg.
           set  bat-abilitato-no  to true.   
           set  bat-bloccante-no  to true.  
           set  bat-bloccabile-no to true.  
           move bat-abilitato  to hid-abil.
           move bat-bloccante  to hid-bloc.
           move bat-bloccabile to hid-bile.

           modify form1-gd-1(riga, 1), cell-data = col-prg.
           modify form1-gd-1(riga, 3), bitmap spunta2-bmp,
                                       bitmap-number = 1,
                                       bitmap-width 20,
